onReport.t.sol
├─ given the contract is paused
│  └─ it should revert
└─ given the contract is not paused
   ├─ when the caller does not have the FORWARDER_ROLE
   │  └─ it should revert
   └─ when the caller has the FORWARDER_ROLE
      ├─ when the the metadata's workflow id is zero
      │  └─ it should revert
      └─ when the metadata's workflow id is not zero
         ├─ when the metadata's workflow ID does not correspond to any of the workflow types
         │  └─ it should revert
         └─ when the metadata's workflow ID is the auction manager workflow
            └─ it should route the performData to the auction contract's performUpkeep function
